    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and she\u2019s been absolutely wonderful to me. It's a solid, reliable car that\u2019s been well-taken care of and is still in great shape for its next adventure. Everything runs smoothly, and it's super comfortable for those longer drives. If you're looking for a dependable vehicle that looks great and drives even better, this is the one! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to see it go to a good home!",
