    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically robust example of BMW's engineering peak, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system. The power is delivered through a tactile Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M-Differential lock, ensuring optimal torque distribution. This specimen has undergone critical preventive maintenance, including rear subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS bulletproofing, addressing the chassis's known harmonic stress points. The suspension geometry remains true to factory specifications, offering the signature communicative hydraulic steering feel and balanced damping characteristics that define the E46 platform. A purist\u2019s configuration, this vehicle is ready for spirited cornering and high-RPM engagement.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used vehicle in good condition. Engine runs well. Interior is clean. Minor cosmetic wear on exterior. Maintenance records available. Title in hand.",
      "price": 29500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
