    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic balance of performance and reliability. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, with only the expected minor evidence of careful use consistent with a well-loved car. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary; the upholstery remains supple and clean, and every electronic feature\u2014from the infotainment system to the climate control\u2014functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car has been treated to a rigorous maintenance schedule, resulting in a smooth, confident ride and a responsive engine that starts perfectly every time. The tires have ample tread remaining, and the brakes provide firm, consistent stopping power. It is a turn-key example, thoroughly inspected and ready for its next owner to enjoy immediately without any immediate service needs.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
