    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm looking to find a new home for my trusty car. It\u2019s been such a reliable ride for me and is still in really solid shape, perfect for someone who wants a dependable vehicle that looks great on the road! I\u2019ve made sure to keep up with the basics, so it's ready to hit the pavement for many more miles. It drives smoothly and has that comfortable, well-loved feel that makes every trip a breeze. I'm sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to absolutely love it! Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come by for a test drive!",
      "price": 31500.0,
