      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound BMW M3 (E92) featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L V8 powerplant. This naturally aspirated engine utilizes eight individual throttle bodies to deliver instantaneous throttle response and a linear power band peaking at an 8,400 RPM redline. Power is sent through a 6-speed manual gearbox to the rear wheels via the M Variable Differential Lock. Critical preventative maintenance has been performed, including the replacement of rod bearings and throttle actuators, ensuring the structural integrity of the rotating assembly. The chassis remains composed with a firm suspension geometry and crisp turn-in, making it an ideal candidate for the discerning driver seeking a visceral, analog performance experience.",
